data.description: Be Home for Christmas and get $5000 toward closing cost. Close with Preferred Lender: Aggressive Mortgage or Veteran Approved Mortgage and receive an additional $2,000 toward closing. Your Dream home is located in the highly sought-after Promenade at Rex Ridge community. This exceptional brick front property offers a plethora of desirable features that are sure to impress your friends and family members. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a grand 2-story foyer, beautiful hardwood floors, and high ceilings that create a sense of elegance and sophistication. The kitchen is perfect for entertaining, boasting quality granite counters and a spacious, functional layout. Additionally, the main floor features a family room with a cozy fireplace, a dining room, and a versatile bonus room that can serve as a flex space or an office. Moving upstairs, you'll discover the massive master bedroom, complete with a sitting area and a huge walk-in closet. In total, there are four large bedrooms and two full bathrooms on the second floor, accommodating the needs of a growing family or providing ample space for guests. On the main floor, there is a half bathroom for added convenience. Outside, you'll find a fenced-in backyard, perfect for privacy or outdoor activities. This property stands out as one of the largest homes currently for sale in Rex, GA, offering plenty of space and comfort for you and your family. Location is key, and this home offers the convenience of being near shopping and dining options, with easy access to I-675 for commuting or exploring the surrounding areas. With its impressive size, exceptional features, and desirable location, this house is sure to attract a lot of attention. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your dream home. Schedule a tour today and see all that this property has to offer!
